To convert SRT subtitles to ASS:
ffmpeg -i input.srt output.ass

To remove the audio track from a file:
ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -c copy -an output.mp4

To join two videos in sequence:
ffmpeg -i video1.mp4 -i video2.mp4 -filter_complex "[0:v][0:a][1:v][1:a]concat=n=2:v=1:a=1" output.mp4.

To grab the last frame from a video:
ffmpeg -sseof -1 -i video.mp4 -frames:v 1 last_frame.jpg

To create a new video from the first 10 seconds of a video:
ffmpeg -i video.mp4 -t 10 -c copy output.mp4

